Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.69,0:00:10.52,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Attention, all trainers.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.11,0:00:16.77,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,Due to today’s bad weather, \N we are closing all outdoor facilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.19,0:00:21.73,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,All trainers, as well as all Pokémon,
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.73,0:00:24.86,Main,Announcer,0,0,0,,please make use \N of our indoor facilities.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.36,0:00:30.31,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Haru, watch out for the mud!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:31.06,0:00:32.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,All right...!
Comment: 10,0:00:32.36,0:00:34.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:34.56,0:00:37.02,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,The water level’s \N way higher than usual.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:37.98,0:00:39.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, dear...
Dialogue: 10,0:00:40.56,0:00:42.98,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,I’ll go check on \N the Koiking upstream!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:42.98,0:00:45.69,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,You go on ahead and \N get these Pokémon to the lobby!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:45.69,0:00:47.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,A-All right!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:47.02,0:00:49.11,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,But don’t push yourself too hard!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:49.11,0:00:50.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Of course! You be careful, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:58.19,0:01:00.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The river’s flowing crazy fast!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:00.61,0:01:02.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Even the bridge was washed away...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:04.61,0:01:05.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Eevee?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:06.77,0:01:08.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What are you doing over there?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:09.44,0:01:11.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’ll save you right away, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:11.77,0:01:14.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Fushigidane, help me out!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:18.02,0:01:21.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Slowly... Slowly, now...
Dialogue: 10,0:01:24.77,0:01:27.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, Eevee! \N You’re safe now!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:29.44,0:01:30.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Wait, Eevee!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:50.27,0:01:51.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:01:51.02,0:01:52.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Windie?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:55.11,0:01:57.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:58.69,0:02:00.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,W-Wait! Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.11,0:02:03.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.23,0:02:06.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Do we... know each other...?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.11,0:02:07.27,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Windie!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.23,0:02:11.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:11.15,0:02:13.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, yes, thank...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.06,0:02:15.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kento?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.27,0:02:15.90,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.65,0:02:18.27,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.94,0:02:34.48,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.48,0:02:35.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:35.15,0:02:36.61,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Your hair’s still wet.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.61,0:02:38.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, sorry...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.56,0:02:39.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You’ve been here \N since yesterday, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:44.36,0:02:47.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I was off work yesterday, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.77,0:02:49.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:51.11,0:02:55.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,So, uh... Sorry that our reunion \N after so long turned out like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.69,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Don’t be.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:57.69,0:02:59.36,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I’m glad to see you’re doing well.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:00.69,0:03:03.86,Main,Human child,0,0,0,,Mommy, there’s something outside!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.06,0:03:08.06,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,That’s gotta be her ex, yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:08.06,0:03:10.15,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:10.15,0:03:13.11,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,He’s not someone {\i1}sketchy,{\i0} is he?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.11,0:03:15.56,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Now, now, Uncle. \N You’re not her dad.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:17.77,0:03:19.81,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,What’s up, Koduck?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:19.81,0:03:22.77,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Bet it’s{dread Koduck} worried \N that he might steal Haru.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.81,0:03:27.48,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,But... I sure didn’t expect this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.48,0:03:27.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.61,0:03:31.31,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,For you to be working \N in a place like this.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:31.31,0:03:34.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,A place like... this?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.11,0:03:37.56,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I mean... Around this time last year, \N you were working crazy hard on presentations...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.56,0:03:40.65,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,...and going all over for work \N wearing high heels. And now...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.65,0:03:45.06,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Now I’m completely drenched, covered in mud, \N and going around wearing sandals and jerseys.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.06,0:03:45.98,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.65,0:03:47.40,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.40,0:03:48.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,No worries.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:00.19,0:04:03.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I{...} became area manager.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.15,0:04:05.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Really? Congratulations!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.15,0:04:06.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.06,0:04:12.81,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Thought I’d reward myself a little, \N so I came here with Windie.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.56,0:04:14.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.77,0:04:19.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It seems like the rain’ll let up tomorrow, \N so enjoy your stay, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:20.90,0:04:22.31,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.48,0:04:30.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What a shock!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.65,0:04:33.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I never would have thought \N Kento would come here!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:39.36,0:04:41.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Oh, the nostalgia!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.11,0:04:43.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I think this is from we went on a trip, \N just the two of us...
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.77,0:04:46.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Look, Koduck.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.86,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What’s that look for?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:48.86,0:04:51.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yes, I went through that phase.{I had this kind of period in my life, too. | What kind of period? She doesn't say. We are just left to assume that whatever is on her screen right now is EXTREMELY different from the Haru Koduck knows. -TLC}
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.98,0:04:55.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kento’s gotten more mature.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.11,0:04:59.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But... he seemed kind of exhausted.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.94,0:05:03.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.31,0:05:09.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The rain’s passed, so tomorrow we should \N give Kento and Windie the time of their lives!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.69,0:05:26.31,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,What’s going on over there?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.31,0:05:29.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, that’s an obstacle course where...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.15,0:05:30.86,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Goodness, all of you...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.86,0:05:33.56,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Is there a rare Pokémon here \N or something?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.73,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,U-Uh... Gotta get back to work!
Comment: 10,0:05:42.94,0:05:42.94,Main,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.11,0:06:03.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Todoggler!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.48,0:06:05.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:15.52,0:06:17.86,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Full of energy, as always...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.48,0:06:26.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:47.48,0:06:48.69,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Let’s eat!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:48.69,0:06:50.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Let’s eat.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.56,0:06:59.61,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,It’s great.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.06,0:07:14.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mizugorou! There, there...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.44,0:07:25.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I got soaked again!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:25.52,0:07:28.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Sorry. I’m just a mess today.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.98,0:07:30.56,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kento? What’s wrong?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.27,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.27,0:07:38.56,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Were you really doing so bad \N that you had to escape to a place like this?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.31,0:07:41.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I’m sorry I never noticed.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:42.15,0:07:43.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Uhh...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.02,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Haru! Can you come \N help sort through these berries?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.02,0:07:49.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, okay! I’ll be right there!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.27,0:07:51.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Sorry, I’ll be right back.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.36,0:07:52.48,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.56,0:07:58.15,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Even in a place like this, \N Haru-san is giving everything her all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Uh, no, I didn’t mean...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.15,0:08:01.98,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.73,0:08:08.02,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Haru-san may be a bit clumsy, but it’s my opinion \N that she is well suited for this kind of work.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:08.44,0:08:12.52,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,Because there’s nobody who thinks \N and cares about others more than her.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:13.31,0:08:16.44,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,She came by early and told me \N Windie’s leg looked terribly dry,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.44,0:08:19.94,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,and so she wanted \N some massage cream for it.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.94,0:08:25.61,Main,Watanabe,0,0,0,,She is a highly adept worker who can notice \N small details that even the trainer would miss.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.61,0:08:26.40,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.65,0:08:30.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And this?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:30.31,0:08:31.36,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,That goes over here.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:31.36,0:08:32.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.27,Main,Alisa,0,0,0,,Same for this one.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.27,0:08:34.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.94,0:08:39.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The view from here is the best!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.94,0:08:41.61,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.61,0:08:44.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I really love this island.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.94,0:08:49.65,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You’re not wrong, \N I basically ran away here at first...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.65,0:08:52.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But now I’m really glad I came.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.02,0:08:54.69,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:55.61,0:08:57.02,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.98,0:09:01.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.19,0:09:03.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,The whole staff built it together!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,It was really hard. \N Took us two wholes months.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But it’s a big hit with the Pokémon!{Literal for this line and the last: "It was really difficult work that took a whole two months to do, but it's incredibly popular with the Pokémon."}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:09.44,0:09:11.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Watch this, Windie.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.19,0:09:17.27,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Woo! Feels great!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.27,0:09:18.98,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.02,0:09:24.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,See? You try it too, Kento, Windie!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:24.61,0:09:26.52,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.52,0:09:30.36,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Geez... Stuff like this \N really makes her act like a kid.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.31,0:09:43.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kento, what was all {\i1}that?{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.61,0:09:45.61,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Don’t laugh...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.02,0:09:56.52,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Koduck, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.52,0:09:57.31,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I’m glad.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.31,0:09:58.02,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.98,0:10:01.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You finally laughed.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:02.86,0:10:05.86,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,It really is fun being with you.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.23,0:10:06.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.27,0:10:11.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What is it, Koduck?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:11.19,0:10:13.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh? Where’s Windie?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.69,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Hmm? Didn’t it{dread Windie} come down \N with Koduck...?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.77,0:10:20.69,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,What’s the big idea, Windie?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.40,0:10:24.02,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,C’mon, I’ll pull you out.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:27.15,0:10:28.36,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.36,0:10:31.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Kento, I think that’s hurting Windie.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:31.36,0:10:32.44,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Sorry, Windie!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:32.44,0:10:35.23,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Oh, I know! If I just put it{dread Windie} back \N in the Monster Ball...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:35.23,0:10:38.44,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Uh... Ball... Ball...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.44,0:10:40.69,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Huh? Where’s the ball?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.02,0:10:43.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Koduck, help me out.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.52,0:10:45.23,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Windie.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.36,0:10:55.23,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I want you to \N relax your muscles, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.02,0:10:58.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Tickle, tickle, tickle...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.61,0:10:59.52,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,How’s that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.52,0:11:03.36,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Tickle, tickle, tickle, \N tickle, tickle, tickle, tickle...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.65,0:11:06.02,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.90,0:11:10.94,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Windie!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:10.94,0:11:12.77,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,What a relief!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Are you okay? \N You’re not hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.98,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Yeah, looks just fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.61,0:11:22.44,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru, what did you do?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.94,0:11:26.19,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,I just made it laugh, \N so that it would stop overexerting itself.{dread Windie x3}{Also there's a lot of "funbaru"-ing here... Which is then CONTRASTED AGAINST "ganbaru". I guess the idea is that funbaru here is like just pressing yourself for the sake of it and not actually getting anywhere, whereas ganbaru-ing is working hard but effectively.}
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.56,0:11:28.02,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Overexerting?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.02,0:11:32.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Windie just now was a lot \N like how I used to be.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.44,0:11:33.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:37.19,0:11:40.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Always working hard, \N trying to refine myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.56,0:11:45.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Struggling like crazy, \N but never actually making any headway.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.61,0:11:49.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But I was really just \N overexerting myself for nothing.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.11,0:11:52.48,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Desperately trying to \N tense up my arms and legs...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.23,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:54.23,0:11:57.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Once I realized that, I thought I’d just \N try and stop overexerting myself.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.15,0:12:01.86,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Let loose all my tension, \N laugh as hard as I could...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.86,0:12:05.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,And then I was able to \N move forward with ease.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.56,0:12:10.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Ever since I came here, \N I haven’t needed to overexert myself...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.44,0:12:13.11,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But because of that, \N I’ve been able to give it my all.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.65,0:12:15.69,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I must say...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.48,0:12:18.27,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,You’re really cool \N the way you are now.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.27,0:12:21.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Huh?! Th-Th-That’s not true at all!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:23.56,0:12:25.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru, I...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.15,0:12:25.86,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.56,0:12:29.40,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Never mind.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.65,0:12:34.36,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,I’m all refreshed, so starting tomorrow, \N I think I’ll be able to give it my all at work.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.36,0:12:36.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Really? That’s great to hear!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right, Windie?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.40,0:12:46.15,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Haru.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.15,0:12:46.81,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:47.77,0:12:48.90,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.61,0:12:52.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,No, thank {\i1}you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:03.06,0:13:04.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,What’s wrong, Koduck?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.44,0:13:14.90,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,There’s a good Windie...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.52,0:13:17.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,You too, Koduck...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.44,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,So, ready to start another day?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.06,0:13:32.73,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,There are sunny days... \N There are rainy days...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.94,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Sometimes even stormy days...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:34.94,0:13:38.61,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,But no matter the weather, \N you can find a way to have fun.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:39.61,0:13:42.77,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Sure, sometimes things just \N don’t turn out the way you want,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.11,0:13:46.40,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,but you can get over it \N if you just keep smiling.{OH NO SHE'S BEEN INFECTED BY PROTAGONIST-KUN 4}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:46.40,0:13:50.90,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Because there are so many \N fun friends here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.90,0:13:52.19,Main,Dan,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.19,0:13:54.06,Main,Tyler,0,0,0,,Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:55.36,0:13:56.48,Main,Kento,0,0,0,,Did you have fun, Windie?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.48,0:13:57.31,Main,Human child,0,0,0,,Bye bye!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:57.31,0:13:58.36,Main,Human child,0,0,0,,Come back sometime!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.02,0:14:06.02,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Let’s have fun together again!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.19,0:14:15.56,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,With all that said...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.36,0:14:17.15,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,Right here...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:17.90,0:14:19.98,Main,Haru,0,0,0,,...is where I am!{Callback to episode 1 and 4, but not an exact quote}
Comment: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:29.65,Main,,0,0,0,,{Ending}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.06,0:14:41.36,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}For so long, I’d been looking for you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:46.11,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}And at last, I found you on this island
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:52.02,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}What a beautiful sunset this is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.02,0:14:56.90,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}I’m glad I got to see it with you
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.81,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When I was alone
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.81,0:15:02.52,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}When I felt lonely
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:07.15,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}I would think of you
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.73,0:15:12.98,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}Teach me, and only me
