Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:23.06,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(0,350)}Let me hear even more of them
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.86,0:15:28.48,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,0)}This is a healing island
