Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.86,0:16:40.11,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Gadgets to bring smiles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.11,0:16:45.11,ED,Yamashita Tatsurou,0,0,0,,{\blur1}Now fill up my heart
